OREGON MESABI CORPORATION, Appellant, v. C. D. JOHNSON LUMBER CORPORATION, Appellee No. 11570. Circuit Court of Appeals Ninth Circuit. Aug. 18, 1948 *641Laing, Gray & Smith, Henry S. Gray, and John R. Becker, all of Portland, Or., for appellant. King, Wood, Miller & Anderson and Robert S. Miller, all of Portland, Or., for appellee.

Before DENMAN, STEPHENS, and HEALY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The motion of appellant to recall the mandate and for modification of judgment is denied for the reasons stated in the denial of a similar motion in 169 F.2d 639, this day filed.
